{
  "stem": "964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll go to this girl, and my friend will go to this girl, and the other girl, and the-- the-- the tailor will go there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we run away lunchtime, And we got at our places.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We figure, well, another day, we'd be gone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Happens so that the Germans pushed back the Russians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we got stuck in between.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We got stuck in between a week, two weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is the field police, like the MP on the frontier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the partisans became very active there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because the Russians were close by, the partisans became very active.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there, these police were looking for partisans-- partisans that didn't have any uniforms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They walked around in plain clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So the-- the people that were hiding us, they-- they say, look here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Germans are looking for-- for-- for partisans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We cannot keep you here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because once they-- they catch us, all of us are going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we didn't put them-- we didn't want to put them in-- in-- in a position that they're going to be killed for us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If they catch us alone, they kill us because we are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they're just-- so we decided-- to the partisans we couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they told us that we should go back about 200 kilometers, 150 kilometers maybe it was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Go back in the back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There's a big, huge industrial complex that used to make freight-- freight cars in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we have no choice, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was no food, and we were in danger, they were in danger.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of their friends, a boy, lead us out to the highway.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
